using Pulumi;
using Aws = Pulumi.Aws;

class MyStack : Stack
{
    public MyStack()
    {

        {
            TargetArn = aws_inspector_assessment_target.Example.Arn,
            Duration = 3600,
            RulesPackageArns =

                "arn:aws:inspector:us-west-2:758058086616:rulespackage/0-9hgA516p",
